\s Ninataka kumsifu Yesu Kristo 
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ninataka kumsifu \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  Kristo\bd*\bd  aliyeondoa dhambi zangu zote. Twende sote sasa tumsifu Yeye, na \bd*\bd Pendo kubwa\bd*\bd  la \bd*\bd Mwokozi\bd*\bd ! \bd*
\pc \bdit Haleluya! Yu Mfalme ’kuu! Haleluya! Asifiwe! Alinisamehe dhambi zote; alinilinda kwa salama! \bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Na baraka yake anaimimina, kama mvua inyeshavyo juu yangu. Nastarehe mikononi mwake \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd , rehema yake inatosha. \bd*
