\zoli1 \bd Siku moja nitamwona \bd*\bd Yesu\bd*\bd  Kristo\bd*\bd  kati’ nchi nzuri sana ya furaha, macho yangu yatamtazama yeye, kuona sura ya Mfalme. \bd*
